RETURN SQL:
target: select T1.name , T1.team_id , max(T2.salary) from team AS T1 join salary AS T2 on T1.team_id = T2.team_id group by T1.team_id;

target: select T2.product_name from problems AS T1 join product AS T2 join staff AS T3 on T1.product_id = T2.product_id and T1.reported_by_staff_id = T3.staff_id where T3.staff_first_name = "Lacey" and T3.staff_last_name = "Bosco" INTERSECT select T2.product_name from problems AS T1 join product AS T2 join staff AS T3 on T1.product_id = T2.product_id and T1.reported_by_staff_id = T3.staff_id where T3.staff_first_name = "Kenton" and T3.staff_last_name = "Champlin"
